html.htmlText: The house was built after renovating an old cabin with an adjoining barn at an altitude of 915 meters above sea level, owned by the “di carulina” family, surrounded by greenery and offers a peaceful stay. During the winter, in case of snow, the accommodation can be reached on foot, walking about 20 minutes.

It is spread over two floors: on the first floor there is a living unit consisting of a bright living room and kitchen (equipped with a dishwasher), double bedroom, bedroom with bunk bed and bathroom with shower: ideal for family holidays; on the second floor there are two independent studios consisting of a kitchen, sofa bed (double) and bathroom: ideal for couples. All units have a wood stove, independent entrances and access to the common outdoor green area. Guests have an exclusive outdoor parking lot 50 meters from the house.

IMPORTANT
The only phone company that receives is TIM. Wi-Fi doesn't always work.
There are no shops or bars.
The nearest town is Gordona and is a 15-minute drive away.

content.htmlText: For those who love canyoning, the mountain guides organize outings to discover the rocky canyons of the Boggia stream. For those who love climbing, Val Bodengo has a very wide range of trails ranging from 5th to 6th grade, with very technical and refined passages, suitable for those who already have some confidence with this discipline. Then there is trekking: starting from here you can reach Alpe Cima, Alpe Piazza, Alpe Garzelli, Alpe Campo or visit Val Pilotera.  There is no shortage of mountain bike itineraries (possibility to rent e-bikes at the Bar San Martino in Gordona).

For those who love canyoning, the mountain guides organize outings to discover the rocky canyons of the Boggia stream. For those who love climbing, Val Bodengo has a very wide range of trails ranging from 5th to 6th grade, with very technical and refined passages, suitable for those who already have some confidence with this discipline. Then there is trekking: starting from here you can reach Alpe Cima, Alpe Piazza, Alpe Garzelli, Alpe Campo or visit Val Pilotera.  There is no shortage of mountain bike itineraries (possibility to rent e-bikes at the Bar San Martino in Gordona).

Getting to Val Bodengo is easy: by car, take the Provincial Trivulzia road to Gordona. From here, follow the signs for the consortium road that climbs up to the Maggengo. Before heading to the Bruciata, however, it is advisable to purchase the authorization for the road, available online https://www.valbodengo.shop/  or in the bars of Gordona.

reviews.comments:
Io e la mia fidanzata cercavamo un soggiorno vicino alla Svizzera 🇨🇭 per escursioni semplici e momenti di relax 🛀 in un weekend di autunno 🍂
Quello che abbiamo trovato è veramente un luogo sorprendente:
Appartamento: interior semplice e curato, ambiente con stufa a legna 🪵 molto pratica. Non manca nulla 🫶🏻
Giardino: erba perfetta, zona barbecue, hot tub nuovissima, panorama sulle montagne e boschi circostanti ✨ vince la cura dei dettagli
Host: super ospitalità, sintesi di gentilezza e comunicazione. Da subito in confidenza, abbiamo respirato l’essenza della famiglia 👨‍👩‍👧‍👧🐕
Bravi 👏🏻🤠

localizedReview.comments:
My fiancée and I were looking for a stay near Switzerland 🇨🇭 for simple excursions and relaxing moments 🛀 on an autumn weekend 🍂
What we found is truly an amazing place:
Apartment: simple and well-kept interior, environment with wood stove 🪵 very practical. There's everything you need 🫶🏻
Garden: perfect grass, barbecue area, brand new hot tub, views of the mountains and surrounding woods attention to detail ✨ is the winner
Host: super hospitality, a combination of kindness and communication. Immediately confident, we breathed the essence of family 👨‍👩‍👧‍👧🐕
Well done 👏🏻🤠

reviews.comments:
Unser Urlaub in dem kleinen Häuschen war traumhaft, man hatte seine absolute Ruhe, da niemand anderes da war und konnte so jederzeit in den Whirlpool springen. Die Wohnung war sehr neu und hatte alles, was man brauchte ohne dabei zu voll gestellt zu sein. Ein Highlight war der Ofen, der im Herbst wunderbar gemütlich einheiztm Die Umgebung selbst ist wunderschön, man hat eine tolle Aussicht auf die Berge und kann direkt vom Haus aus Wanderungen starten. Der Ort im Tal, Chiavenna, ist ebenfalls einen Besuch wert, ansonsten sind wir einfach in der kleinen Ruheoase geblieben. Wlan-Empfang hat nicht ganz in unsere Wohnung gereicht, aber das war auch nicht notwendig.
Wir waren rundum zufrieden und kommen bestimmt nochmal wieder!

localizedReview.comments:
Our vacation in the little house was fantastic, you had absolute peace and quiet, since no one else was there and you could jump into the hot tub at any time. The apartment was very new and had everything you needed without being too crowded. A highlight was the oven, which heats up wonderfully cozy in the fall. The surroundings themselves are beautiful, you have a great view of the mountains and can start hikes directly from the house. The place in the valley, Chiavenna, is also worth a visit, otherwise we just stayed in the small oasis of peace. Wi-Fi reception did not quite reach our apartment, but that was not necessary.
We were completely satisfied and will definitely come back!

reviews.comments: Freundliche Gastgeberin, schöne Wohnung, gerne wieder :-)

localizedReview.comments: Friendly hostess, nice apartment, glad to come back :-)

reviews.comments:
Un piccolo alloggio , confortevole e rilassante, ottimo se state cercando un posto dove staccare dalla tecnologia e lo stress moderno.
Chiara e suo marito sono carinissimi e super disponibili, li vicino partono molte passeggiate (molto semplici ma con ottimi paesaggi).
Consigliatissimo per chi come detto in precedenza voglia godersi qualche giorno lontano dallo stress del giorno d'oggi. La casa è esattamente come riportata nelle foto, la piscina riscaldata è molto piacevole soprattutto alla sera dove è possibile godere di stelle e paesaggi sconfinati

localizedReview.comments:
A small, comfortable and relaxing accommodation, great if you're looking for a place to disconnect from technology and modern stress.
Chiara and her husband are very nice and super helpful, there are many walks nearby (very simple but with great landscapes).
Highly recommended for those who, as mentioned above, want to enjoy a few days away from the stress of today. The house is exactly as shown in the photos, the heated pool is very pleasant especially in the evening where you can enjoy stars and boundless landscapes

reviews.comments:
נכס יפה במיקום שקט בהרים עם ג׳קוזי ומנגל בחצר. המארחים אדיבים וזמינים.
לקחת בחשבון שאין קליטה סלולרית וה-WIFI רוב הזמן לא עבד והחניה לרכב רחוקה מהדירה- יש הליכה של בערך 200 מ׳ בעלייה חדה. הנסיעה בכביש היחיד שמגיע אל הנכס דורשת אגרה מה שלא צויין מראש. הניקיון היה טוב סך הכל אך הכלים במטבח דרשו ניקיון נוסף. סך הכל החוויה הייתה טובה ונהנינו מהשהייה.

localizedReview.comments:
A beautiful property in a quiet location in the mountains with a hot tub and a barbecue in the yard. Hosts are kind and available.
Take into account that there is no cell service and theWiFi most of the time did not work and the parking for the car is far from the apartment- there is a walk of about 200 meters on a sharp rise. The only road trip that goes to the property requires a toll which is not specified in advance. The cleanliness was good overall but the dishes in the kitchen required extra cleaning. Overall the experience was good and we enjoyed the stay.

reviews.comments: Fantastic accommodation with hikes and natural pools nearby. Chiara was a very friendly host. Recommended! We will be back.

Die Unterkunft liegt mitten in den Bergen, direkt an einem Fluss (auch zum Baden geeignet). Alles ist modern und sauber. Das Grundstück ist riesig und wunderschön.
Chiara ist eine tolle Gastgeberin und sehr nett. Sie hat uns super Tipps gegeben und war sehr zuvorkommend.

localizedReview.comments:
The accommodation is located in the middle of the mountains, right on a river (also suitable for swimming). Everything is modern and clean. The property is huge and beautiful.
Chiara is a great host and very nice. She gave us great tips and was very accommodating.

reviews.comments: Very carrying and kind hosts. The place is managed with lots of love and great detail. Thank you!

Hervorragende, sehr freundliche und sympathische Gastgeber, stets erreichbar und haben sich sofort um meine Anliegen gekümmert.
Die Wohnung ist sehr gepflegt und sauber! Kann ich jederzeit gerne weiterempfehlen.

localizedReview.comments:
Excellent, very friendly and likeable hosts, always available and took care of my concerns immediately.
The apartment is very well maintained and clean! I would be happy to recommend it.

reviews.comments:
Chiara a été une hôte formidable. Très accueillante et chaleureuse lors de notre arrivée et toujours super réactive. Le logement est juste sublime, perdu dans la nature, c’est un vrai havre de paix.
Merci à Chiara pour cette expérience unique!

localizedReview.comments:
Chiara was a great host. Very welcoming and warm when we arrived and always super responsive. The place is just sublime, lost in nature, it's a real haven of peace.
Thanks to Chiara for this unique experience!

reviews.comments: Super Lage Super Leute, sehr entspannt!

localizedReview.comments: Great location Great people very chilled!

reviews.comments: Die Wohnung ist klein aber fein. Der hotpot unter dem sternenhimmel war grandios. Chiara und Andrea sind super nett und unkompliziert.

localizedReview.comments: The apartment is small, but nice. The hotpot under the stars was great. Chiara and Andrea are super nice and straightforward.

reviews.comments: We had a wonderful week in the accommodation of Chiara. Chiara was a wonderful host and the house, the garden and the entire surroundings were a dream! Grazie mille Chiara :)

Big recommendation
The room was a bit poorly-sound insulated though, but not a big deal
Thanks Chiara! :)

Meine Zeit in dieser wundervollen Unterkunft war hervorragend!
Diese Unterkunft ist etwas besonderes , das Flair, die Natur und die Gastgeberin und ihre Familie sind einzigartig.
Das Haus und das Grundstück sind sehr idyllisch, man hat Ruhe und kann sehr gut entspannen. Die Natur und die Berge rundherum sind eine Augenweide. Man kann sehr gut wandern. Ganz unmittelbar in der Nähe kann man sogar in kaltem Bergwasser baden. Es ist einzigartig.
Die Unterkunft war klein und sehr sehr schön ausgestattet. Alles was man braucht ich vorhanden. Die Ausstattung ist sehr hochwertig, neu und sehr sauber.
Sehr schöne Details, mit viel Gefühl für Naturverbundenheit und mit Liebe , ausgewählt.
Man hat im Garten die Möglichkeit zu grillen und ein beheizter Whirlpool steht mitten auf dem Grundstück.
Die Gastgeberin und ihre Familie war sehr freundlich, herzlich, hilfsbereit und immer erreichbar.
Der aufregende Weg zur Unterkunft auf 950 Meter Höhe war für mich ein extra tolles Erlebnis.
Vielen Dank!

localizedReview.comments:
My time in this wonderful place was outstanding!
This home is special , the flair, nature and the hostess and her family are unique.
The house and the property are very idyllic, you have peace and quiet and can relax very well. Nature and mountains all around are a feast for the eyes. It is possible to hike very well. Nearby you can even bathe in cold mountain water. It's unique.
The place was small and very very nicely equipped. Everything you need is available. The amenities are very high quality, new and very clean.
Very nice details, selected with a lot of sense for closeness to nature and with love.
You have the possibility to grill in the garden and a heated hot tub is in the middle of the property.
The host and her family were very friendly, warm, helpful and always available.
The exciting way to get to the property at 950 meters was an extra great experience for me.
Thanks to you!

reviews.comments: Wir haben das Grundstück sowie die Wohnung unheimlich genossen und wären gern länger geblieben. Sehr hilfsbereite und herzliche Familie. Eine wahnsinnige Stille inmitten der wunderschöner Natur. Wir kommen definitiv wieder! Desiree und Philipp p.s:trittsicher sollte man sein ☺️

localizedReview.comments: We enjoyed the property as well as the apartment incredibly and would have liked to have stayed longer. Very helpful and warm family. An insane silence in the middle of beautiful nature. We will definitely be back! Desiree and Philipp p.s: you should be sure ☺️

reviews.comments: Bellissime persone, gentili, alla mano, molto disponibili, esperienza da rifare assolutamente.

localizedReview.comments: Beautiful people, kind, helpful, very helpful, experience to redo absolutely.

reviews.comments:
se volete sapere cosa significa essere ospitati da un super host, prendetevi qualche giorno per andare a trovare Chiara. i servizi offerti, dalla vasca idromassaggio esterna al barbecue, sono eccellenti; l'ampio prato esterno è ideale per rilassarsi, leggere e prendere il sole; la piccola casa è pulita con amore e rispetto.
consigliatissimo

localizedReview.comments:
if you want to know what it means to be hosted by a super host, take a few days to visit Chiara. The services offered, from the outdoor hot tub to the barbecue, are excellent; the large outdoor lawn is ideal for relaxing, reading and sunbathing; the small house is clean with love and respect.
highly recommended

reviews.comments: We spend some amazing days at the cabin. The host was really nice and always helpful. Thank you so much!

Chiara hat zusammen mit ihrer Familie ein kleines Paradies im Val Bodengo geschaffen, welches sie gerne mit ihren Gästen teilt, z.B. Hotpot benutzen, Hühner füttern. Wir haben uns äusserst willkommen gefühlt und haben diesen wunderbaren Ort mitten in der Natur sehr genossen. Das Appartement ist sehr stilvoll und gemütlich eingerichtet. Einziger Wermutstropfen - ist die Nachbarswohung belegt, ist es etwas hellhörig. Wir kommen auf jeden Fall wieder!

localizedReview.comments: Chiara, together with her family, has created a small paradise in the Val Bodengo, which she likes to share with their guests, such as using the hotpot, feeding chickens. We felt extremely welcome and enjoyed this wonderful place in the middle of nature. The apartment is very stylish and cozy. The only downer - if the neighboring apartment is occupied, it's a bit noisy. We will definitely be back!

reviews.comments: Herrlicher Fluss ( bekannt für Canioning) lädt zur Abkühlung in den frischen Pozzis ein. Das Jacuzzi ist in mitten der Berge ein herrlicher Ort um ein paar Stunden und Aperitivo zu verweilen. Mir wurde an meinem Geburtstag sogar ein hübsches Sträusschen Blumen gebracht. Sehr hilfsbereite freundliche Familie, sehr entspannter Aufenthalt. Kommen jeder Zeit gerne wieder!

localizedReview.comments: Magnificent river ( known for Canioning) invites you to cool off in the fresh Pozzis. The jacuzzi is a wonderful place to stay in the middle of the mountains for a few hours and aperitivo. I was even brought a pretty little bit of flowers on my birthday. Very helpful friendly family, very relaxed stay. We will be happy to come back any time!

reviews.comments:
Die Unterkunft ist sehr schön. Man hat seine Ruhe und kann gut entspannen. Chiara und ihre Familie sind unfassbar gastfreundlich und zuvorkommend.
Wir haben uns sehr wohl gefühlt und werden definitiv nochmal kommen.
Eine klare Empfehlung!!

localizedReview.comments:
The property is very nice. You have your peace and can relax well. Chiara and her family are incredibly welcoming and accommodating.
We felt very comfortable and will definitely come again.
A clear recommendation!!

reviews.comments:
Sehr schön und ruhig gelegen.
Das Gebäude war in der oberen Wohnung sehr hellhörig.
Der Aufstieg vom Parkplatz zum Haus ist sehr steil.

localizedReview.comments:
Very nice and quiet location.
The building was very noisy in the upper apartment.
The ascent from the parking lot to the house is very steep.

reviews.comments: Schön ruhige Lage, genau das was wir wollten

localizedReview.comments: Beautifully quiet location, exactly what we wanted

reviews.comments: Es ist ein wahres Paradies, das Chiara und ihre Familie in Bruciata geschaffen haben. Die Wohnung, der Ausblick, die malerische Umgebung sowie der Whirlpool: Es ist einfach alles perfekt. Hier in der Natur kann man richtig zur Ruhe kommen. Chiara, ihr Mann und die beiden Töchter sind unglaublich aufmerksame und liebenswürdige Gastgeber. Wir haben uns wahnsinnig wohl gefühlt und werden definitiv wiederkommen. Höchste Empfehlung und 10 von 10 Sternen! Liebe Grüße und bis bald, Silja und Noah

localizedReview.comments: It's a truly amazing paradise that Chiara and her family created in Bruciata. The apartment, the view, the picturesque surroundings and the hot tub: everything is just perfect. Here in nature you can really relax. Chiara, her husband and the two daughters are incredibly attentive and gracious hosts. We felt incredibly comfortable and will definitely be back. Highest recommendation and 10 out of 10 stars! Best regards and see you soon, Silja and Noah

reviews.comments:
Ein sehr schöner Ort, der zum verweilen, entspannen und geniessen einlädt.
Die Gastgeber sind sehr freundlich, zuvorkommend und bei Fragen immer da.

localizedReview.comments:
A very nice place that invites you to linger, relax and enjoy.
The hosts are very friendly, courteous and always there with questions.

reviews.comments: Chiara was a good host, of There was somerhing we knew how to contact her. The house was perfect, surrouded by nature.

Monolocale nuovo e curato in ogni dettaglio, ideale per coppie e soggiorni di più giorni, per staccare la spina e rilassarsi al fresco e nel verde della montagna! Prato verde con sdraio e tavolo per pranzare fuori, all’ombra di una betulla. Il materasso comodo pur essendo un divanoletto!

localizedReview.comments: New studio with attention to detail, ideal for couples and multi-day stays, to unplug and relax in the fresh air and green of the mountain! Green lawn with deckchair and dining table outside, in the shade of a birch tree. The mattress is comfortable while being a sofa bed!

reviews.comments: Beautiful and cozy place, great hosts, super friendly and helpful. Thank you for a wonderful time!

The place is absolutely wonderful within beautiful surroundings! The apartment is stylish and very clean! Andrea and his family have been the perfect hosts. We had an amazing time. We highly recommend it!

Il posto è esattamente come ci si aspetta dalla descrizione, isolato quanto basta per staccare la spina dalla vita quotidiana. L'appartamento è attrezzato perfettamente per trascorrerci in tutta comodità il soggiorno, a pochissimi kilometri da delle passeggiate rilassanti e appaganti sia da un punto di vista della bellezza del paesaggio che dell'immersione nella natura.
Host ospitali, disponibili e simpaticissimi, sempre pronti a consigliarmi o aiutarmi in caso di necessità.
Consiglio vivamente questo posto nel caso vogliate prendervi una pausa dallo stress quotidiano e svegliarvi con una vista della montagna, perfettamente immerso nella natura.

localizedReview.comments:
Place is exactly as expected from the description, just set aside just to unwind from everyday life. The apartment is perfectly equipped to spend the stay in comfort, just a few kilometers from the relaxing and fulfilling walks both from a view of the beauty of the landscape and the immersion in nature.
Hospitable, helpful and very nice hosts, always ready to recommend or help me if needed.
I highly recommend this place in case you want to take a break from everyday stress and wake up with a view of the mountain, perfectly immersed in nature.

reviews.comments:
Luogo rilassante, immerso nella natura: verde, montagne, torrenti e percorsi. Ideale per chi vuole staccare la spina da tutto e da tutti.
Ospitalità unica. Andrea e Chiara, insieme alle figlie, ci hanno accolto calorosamente e ci hanno fatto sentire come in famiglia. Sono sempre stati a nostra disposizione.
5 stelle a tutto.

localizedReview.comments:
Relaxing place, surrounded by nature: green, mountains, streams and paths. Ideal for those who want to disconnect from everything and everyone.
Unique hospitality. Andrea and Chiara, along with their daughters, welcomed us warmly and made us feel like family. They've always been there for us.
5 stars for everything.

reviews.comments: Andrea and Chiara are the perfect hosts. Always available for everything needed and respect your privacy 100%. The apartments are brand new and extremely clean. Everything is functioning and equipped with all the basics. The garden is beautiful and we enjoyed being able have breakfast outside every morning. On a clear night you can see an amazing night sky, priceless and simply amazing. The location is perfect for hikers as one of the hiking trails crosses the property and there is also the option to do canyoning tours. The river is right in front of the property and at five minutes walking distance there are areas were you can swim and dive into the river. The restaurants down in the valley offer delicious dishes made with local products.  Highly recommended if you want to get away from the stress of the city and get immerse in a pristine and peaceful environment.
